reviews.text: Great food. Best service I’ve had in HK so far. Wonderful view at dinner time to see the lightening of the other side of the harbor :) Kids enjoyed the nice atmosphere and stunning view as well!

Very nice place, and food is great as well as the service, view at 101 is just fabulous, even the price is higher but definitely worth it, sirely want to come back if any chance. By the way, a must also visit area - toilet, has a such super 'pee-view', just like the one at Peninsula...
Real good lunch for my birthday, not cheap but the Victoria harbor view would worth it.
Stunning view, with highest quality Chinese dinner
